description: List the Remote Desktop Services (RDS) License Server endpoints.

parameters.name: Filters
parameters.description: You can use the following filters to streamline results: IdentityProviderArn (dict) --- A filter name and value pair that is used to return more specific results from a describe or list operation. You can use filters can be used to match a set of resources by specific criteria, such as tags, attributes, or IDs. Attribute (string) --- The name of an attribute to use as a filter. Operation (string) --- The type of search (For example, eq, geq, leq) Value (string) --- Value of the filter.

nested_items.name: LicenseServerEndpoints
nested_items.description: An array of LicenseServerEndpoint resources that contain detailed information about the RDS License Servers that meet the request criteria.

nested_items.name: CreationTime
nested_items.description: The timestamp when License Manager created the license server endpoint.

nested_items.name: IdentityProviderArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the identity provider that's associated with the RDS license server endpoint.

nested_items.name: LicenseServerEndpointArn
nested_items.description: The ARN of the ServerEndpoint resource for the RDS license server.

nested_items.name: LicenseServerEndpointId
nested_items.description: The ID of the license server endpoint.

nested_items.name: LicenseServerEndpointProvisioningStatus
nested_items.description: The current state of the provisioning process for the RDS license server endpoint.

nested_items.name: LicenseServers
nested_items.description: An array of LicenseServer resources that represent the license servers that are accessed through this endpoint.

nested_items.name: HealthStatus
nested_items.description: The health status of the RDS license server.

nested_items.name: Ipv4Address
nested_items.description: A list of domain IPv4 addresses that are used for the RDS license server.

nested_items.name: ProvisioningStatus
nested_items.description: The current state of the provisioning process for the RDS license server.

nested_items.name: ServerEndpoint
nested_items.description: The ServerEndpoint resource contains the network address of the RDS license server endpoint.

nested_items.name: Endpoint
nested_items.description: The network address of the endpoint.

nested_items.name: StatusMessage
nested_items.description: The message associated with the provisioning status, if there is one.

nested_items.name: NextToken
nested_items.description: The next token used for paginated responses. When this field isn't empty, there are additional elements that the service hasn't included in this request. Use this token with the next request to retrieve additional objects.
